      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="117.txt-2">
      <text>Heads borne singly or in ± tight clusters, short-pedunculate, closely subtended and often overtopped by basal and large cauline leaves.</text>
      <structure id="o441" name="head">
        <character name="arrangement" value="singly" />
